compareParameters.CP_TABLE_LIST_QUERY: SELECT TABLE_SCHEMA, TABLE_NAME, STR_TO_DATE(date_format(current_timestamp(),'%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') AS LOG_CREATED_ON, coalesce(has_created_on_col, 0) as HAS_CREATED_ON_COL FROM information_schema.TABLES t left outer join (SELECT table_name as table_col, case when count(*) > 0 then '1' else '0' end as has_created_on_col FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS WHERE UPPER(COLUMN_NAME) = 'CREATED_ON' group by table_name) c on t.table_name = c.table_col where (TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-consumer-%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-contact-record-%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-contacts-%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-task-%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'task-%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-ecms-%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-enrollment%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-blats%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-plan-provider%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-event%' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-tenant-manager' or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-cti%') and TABLE_SCHEMA not like 'mars-blats1-camunda%' and TABLE_NAME not like 'AUDIT_LOG' and TABLE_NAME not like 'GRID' and TABLE_NAME not like 'GRID_COLUMNS' and TABLE_NAME not like 'GRID_COLUMN_PROPERTIES' and TABLE_NAME not like 'SECTION' and TABLE_NAME not like 'UI_PERMISSIONS' and TABLE_NAME not like 'PAGE' and TABLE_NAME not like 'PORTFOLIO' and TABLE_NAME not like 'PRIVACY_NOTICE' and TABLE_NAME not like 'flyway_schema_history' and TABLE_NAME not like 'USER_SECURITY' and concat(TABLE_SCHEMA,TABLE_NAME) not like 'mars-consumer-%CONSUMER_AUTHENTICATION' -- and table_rows > 0 order by 2;

extractionParameters.INCLUDE_TABLES: mars-consumer-%.%, mars-contact-record-%.%, mars-contacts-%.%, mars-task-%.%, mars-ecms-%.%, mars-enrollment%.%, mars-blats%.%, mars-plan-provider%.%, mars-event%.%, mars-tenant-manager.%,task-%.%
extractionParameters.IGNORE_TABLES: mars-consumer-v2%.%, mars-cti-%.%, mars-etl-%.%, mars-bpm%.%, mars-rules.%, mars-blats1-camunda%.%, mars-tm-config.%, mars-%.%_TRANSACTION, mars-%.AUDIT_LOG, mars-%.DATE_FIELD, mars-%.DISPLAY_LABEL, mars-%.GRID, mars-%.GRID_COLUMNS, mars-%.GRID_COLUMN_PROPERTIES, mars-%.SECTION, mars-%.TASK_TEMPLATE_TYPE_MAP, mars-%.UI_PERMISSIONS, mars-%.FIELDS, mars-%.PAGE, mars-%.USER_ACTIVITY_DETAILS, mars-%.TASK_SEARCH, mars-%.PROJECT_CONFIGURATIONS, mars-%.CASELOADER_PAYLOAD, mars-%.PORTFOLIO, mars-%.PRIVACY_NOTICE, mars-%.TASK_QUEUE_FILTER, mars-%.TASK_QUEUE_FILTER_SCOPE, mars-%.TASK_QUEUE_FILTER_TASK_TYPES, mars-%.TASK_FIELD, mars-%.TASK_TEMPLATE, mars-%.TASK_TEMPLATE_FIELD, mars-%.TASK_TYPE_PERMISSION, mars-%.FIELD_VALIDATION, mars-%.USER_SECURITY, mars-%.flyway_schema_history, mars-%.HOLIDAY_HISTORY, mars-%.CONTACT_RECORD_EDIT_HISTORY, mars-consumer-%.CONSUMER_AUTHENTICATION, mars-%.EXTERNAL_REQ_RESPONSE, mars-%.TRANSACTIONS, mars-%.USER_SECURITY, mars-%.BUSINESS_DAYS, mars-%.BUSINESS_DAYS_HISTORY, mars-%.%BKP% ,mars-%.%_TEMP_%, mars-%.%_TEMP, mars-contact-record-%.CALL_DATA, mars-contact-record-%.CTI_ENTITY, mars-contact-record-%.META_DATA
